# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in values as needed.

```bash
cp .env.example .env.local
```

## Contact Form

```env
# Email address to receive contact form submissions
CONTACT_EMAIL=maliksaddique139@gmail.com

# Optional: Resend API key for email delivery
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxx
```

## Notes

- Without `RESEND_API_KEY`, contact form submissions are validated and logged server-side.
- To enable email delivery, install `resend` and uncomment the Resend block in `src/app/api/contact/route.ts`.
